A family in a studio apartment receives a visit from her husband's brother from another city. Night has fallen, it's time to go to bed. There is only one bed, they put a relative with them. In the morning, in the kitchen, a man talks to his brother:
- Well, how did you sleep?
Brother:
- It's fine, but your wife is weird, she held my dick all night.
The man answers:
- No, it's not my wife, I was holding your dick.
- Trust but check, brother!
